            "Saved: figs_pub/FIG_main_AB_vs_BA_tight.png\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "def seasonal_factor(day, period_days=365, amp=0.6, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (day / period_days) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal_factor(step, steps_per_day, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Smooth day-night UV cycle (clipped to >=0).\n",
        "    phase=-pi/2 makes it start near 0 and peak mid-day.\n",
        "    Returns in [0, 1+amp] roughly, then clipped.\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (step / steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def simulate_year(\n",
        "    days=365,\n",
        "    steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "    x0=0.20,\n",
        "    xmin=0.15,\n",
        "    a=3.0,\n",
        "    b=2.0,\n",
        "    chiral_bias=0.01,\n",
        "    chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    uv_phase=0.0,\n",
        "    a_phase=0.0,\n",
        "    K=10.0,\n",
        "):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "\n",
        "    aL0 = a * (1.0 + chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"growth\", \"both\") else a\n",
        "    aR0 = a * (1.0 - chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"growth\", \"both\") else a\n",
        "    bL0 = b * (1.0 - chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"damage\", \"both\") else b\n",
        "    bR0 = b * (1.0 + chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"damage\", \"both\") else b\n",
        "\n",
        "    xL = float(x0)\n",
        "    xR = float(x0)\n",
        "\n",
        "    xL_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    xR_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    adv_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Store daily mean UV and daily peak UV (useful for plotting)\n",
        "    uv_mean_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    uv_peak_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    a_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        uv_season = seasonal_factor(day, period_days=days, amp=seasonal_uv_amp, phase=uv_phase)\n",
        "        a_mult    = seasonal_factor(day, period_days=days, amp=seasonal_a_amp, phase=a_phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "        aL = aL0 * a_mult\n",
        "        aR = aR0 * a_mult\n",
        "\n",
        "        uv_samples = []\n",
        "\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "\n",
        "            uv_diurnal = diurnal_factor(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp)\n",
        "            uv_inst = uv_season * uv_diurnal\n",
        "            uv_samples.append(uv_inst)\n",
        "\n",
        "            bL = bL0 * uv_inst\n",
        "            bR = bR0 * uv_inst\n",
        "\n",
        "            if gate == \"A\":\n",
        "                if xL >= xmin and K > 0:\n",
        "                    xL += (aL * xL * (1.0 - xL / K)) * dt\n",
        "                if xR >= xmin and K > 0:\n",
        "                    xR += (aR * xR * (1.0 - xR / K)) * dt\n",
        "            else:\n",
        "                xL -= (bL * xL) * dt\n",
        "                xR -= (bR * xR) * dt\n",
        "\n",
        "            if xL < 0.0: xL = 0.0\n",
        "            if xR < 0.0: xR = 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "        uv_samples = np.array(uv_samples, dtype=float)\n",
        "        uv_mean_daily[day] = float(np.mean(uv_samples))\n",
        "        uv_peak_daily[day] = float(np.max(uv_samples))\n",
        "        a_daily[day] = a_mult\n",
        "\n",
        "        xL_daily[day] = xL\n",
        "        xR_daily[day] = xR\n",
        "        adv_daily[day] = xL - xR\n",
        "\n",
        "    return xL_daily, xR_daily, adv_daily, uv_mean_daily, uv_peak_daily, a_daily\n",
        "\n",
        "def save_run(tag, xL, xR, adv, uv_mean, uv_peak, a_mult):\n",
        "    days = np.arange(len(xL))\n",
        "\n",
        "    # NPZ\n",
        "    np.savez(\n",
        "        f\"{tag}_year_run_data.npz\",\n",
        "        xL_daily=xL, xR_daily=xR, adv_daily=adv,\n",
        "        uv_mean_daily=uv_mean, uv_peak_daily=uv_peak,\n",
        "        a_daily=a_mult\n",
        "    )\n",
        "\n",
        "    # CSV\n",
        "    df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "        \"day\": days,\n",
        "        \"xL\": xL,\n",
        "        \"xR\": xR,\n",
        "        \"adv\": adv,\n",
        "        \"uv_mean\": uv_mean,\n",
        "        \"uv_peak\": uv_peak,\n",
        "        \"a_mult\": a_mult\n",
        "    })\n",
        "    df.to_csv(f\"{tag}_year_run_timeseries.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Saved:\", f\"{tag}_year_run_data.npz\", \"and\", f\"{tag}_year_run_timeseries.csv\")\n",
        "    print(\"Final day:\", df.tail(1).to_dict(orient=\"records\")[0])\n",
        "\n",
        "# ---- parameters ----\n",
        "params = dict(\n",
        "    days=365,\n",
        "    steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "    x0=0.20,\n",
        "    xmin=0.15,\n",
        "    a=3.0,\n",
        "    b=2.0,\n",
        "    chiral_bias=0.01,\n",
        "    chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    K=10.0,\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# AB\n",
        "xL_ab, xR_ab, adv_ab, uvmean_ab, uvpeak_ab, am_ab = simulate_year(**params, protocol=\"AB\")\n",
        "save_run(\"AB_diurnal\", xL_ab, xR_ab, adv_ab, uvmean_ab, uvpeak_ab, am_ab)\n",
        "\n",
        "# BA\n",
        "xL_ba, xR_ba, adv_ba, uvmean_ba, uvpeak_ba, am_ba = simulate_year(**params, protocol=\"BA\")\n",
        "save_run(\"BA_diurnal\", xL_ba, xR_ba, adv_ba, uvmean_ba, uvpeak_ba, am_ba)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "ghMXcOhM0eie",
        "outputId": "a6307006-cb09-4f5e-8484-3932d03caf30"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Saved: AB_diurnal_year_run_data.npz and AB_diurnal_year_run_timeseries.csv\n",
            "Final day: {'day': 364, 'xL': 7.854611390767191e-128, 'xR': 9.835734432904972e-136, 'adv': 7.854611292409847e-128, 'uv_mean': 0.989671986306499, 'uv_peak': 1.9793439726129978, 'a_mult': 1.0}\n",
            "Saved: BA_diurnal_year_run_data.npz and BA_diurnal_year_run_timeseries.csv\n",
            "Final day: {'day': 364, 'xL': 3.644468049977069e-158, 'xR': 2.324824059807469e-161, 'adv': 3.642143225917261e-158, 'uv_mean': 0.989671986306499, 'uv_peak': 1.9793439726129978, 'a_mult': 1.0}\n"

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "AB_CSV = \"AB_diurnal_year_run_timeseries.csv\"\n",
        "BA_CSV = \"BA_diurnal_year_run_timeseries.csv\"\n",
        "\n",
        "ab = pd.read_csv(AB_CSV).sort_values(\"day\").reset_index(drop=True)\n",
        "ba = pd.read_csv(BA_CSV).sort_values(\"day\").reset_index(drop=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "for df, name in [(ab, \"AB\"), (ba, \"BA\")]:\n",
        "    for col in [\"day\", \"xL\", \"adv\", \"uv_mean\", \"uv_peak\"]:\n",
        "        if col not in df.columns:\n",
        "            raise ValueError(f\"{name} missing column: {col}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "eps = 1e-12\n",
        "zoom_max_day = 70\n",
        "\n",
        "abz = ab[ab[\"day\"] <= zoom_max_day]\n",
        "baz = ba[ba[\"day\"] <= zoom_max_day]\n",
        "\n",
        "def panel_label(ax, s):\n",
        "    ax.text(0.01, 0.98, s, transform=ax.transAxes, va=\"top\", ha=\"left\",\n",
        "            fontsize=12, fontweight=\"bold\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def cum_pos_adv(series):\n",
        "    return np.cumsum(np.maximum(series, 0.0))\n",
        "\n",
        "ab_cum = cum_pos_adv(ab[\"adv\"].values)\n",
        "ba_cum = cum_pos_adv(ba[\"adv\"].values)\n",
        "\n",
        "max_x = max(ab[\"xL\"].max(), ba[\"xL\"].max())\n",
        "min_x = max(eps, min(\n",
        "    ab.loc[ab[\"xL\"] > 0, \"xL\"].min() if (ab[\"xL\"] > 0).any() else eps,\n",
        "    ba.loc[ba[\"xL\"] > 0, \"xL\"].min() if (ba[\"xL\"] > 0).any() else eps\n",
        "))\n",
        "\n",
        "adv_max = max(ab[\"adv\"].abs().max(), ba[\"adv\"].abs().max())\n",
        "adv_max = adv_max if adv_max > 0 else 1.0\n",
        "\n",
        "fig, axs = plt.subplots(2, 3, figsize=(12.5, 7.2))\n",
        "axs = axs.ravel()\n",
        "\n",
        "# (a) Forcing: show mean and peak UV (diurnal now visible!)\n",
        "ax = axs[0]\n",
        "ax.plot(ab[\"day\"], ab[\"uv_mean\"], label=\"UV mean (daily)\")\n",
        "ax.plot(ab[\"day\"], ab[\"uv_peak\"], linestyle=\"--\", label=\"UV peak (daily)\")\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Day\"); ax.set_ylabel(\"UV level\")\n",
        "ax.set_title(\"Seasonal + diurnal UV forcing\")\n",
        "ax.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "ax.legend(fontsize=9)\n",
        "panel_label(ax, \"a\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# (b) Growth early (log): xL only\n",
        "ax = axs[1]\n",
        "ax.plot(abz[\"day\"], np.maximum(abz[\"xL\"], eps), label=\"AB xL\")\n",
        "ax.plot(baz[\"day\"], np.maximum(baz[\"xL\"], eps), label=\"BA xL\")\n",
        "ax.set_yscale(\"log\")\n",
        "ax.set_ylim(min_x, max_x)\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Day\"); ax.set_ylabel(\"x (log)\")\n",
        "ax.set_title(f\"Growth (log), early (0–{zoom_max_day})\")\n",
        "ax.grid(True, which=\"both\", linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "ax.legend(fontsize=9)\n",
        "panel_label(ax, \"b\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# (c) Advantage early\n",
        "ax = axs[2]\n",
        "ax.plot(abz[\"day\"], abz[\"adv\"], label=\"AB adv\")\n",
        "ax.plot(baz[\"day\"], baz[\"adv\"], label=\"BA adv\")\n",
        "ax.axhline(0, linewidth=0.7)\n",
        "ax.set_ylim(-0.05*adv_max, 1.05*adv_max)\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Day\"); ax.set_ylabel(\"adv\")\n",
        "ax.set_title(f\"Advantage, early (0–{zoom_max_day})\")\n",
        "ax.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "ax.legend(fontsize=9)\n",
        "panel_label(ax, \"c\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# (d) Cumulative advantage (AOI-like)\n",
        "ax = axs[3]\n",
        "ax.plot(ab[\"day\"], ab_cum, label=\"AB cum[adv+]\")\n",
        "ax.plot(ba[\"day\"], ba_cum, label=\"BA cum[adv+]\")\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Day\"); ax.set_ylabel(\"cumulative adv+\")\n",
        "ax.set_title(\"Cumulative advantage (AOI-like)\")\n",
        "ax.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "ax.legend(fontsize=9)\n",
        "panel_label(ax, \"d\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# (e) Phase portrait: use UV_peak so loops appear\n",
        "ax = axs[4]\n",
        "ax.scatter(ab[\"uv_peak\"], ab[\"adv\"], s=14, alpha=0.7, label=\"AB\")\n",
        "ax.scatter(ba[\"uv_peak\"], ba[\"adv\"], s=14, alpha=0.7, label=\"BA\")\n",
        "ax.axhline(0, linewidth=0.7)\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"UV peak (daily)\"); ax.set_ylabel(\"adv\")\n",
        "ax.set_title(\"Advantage vs UV (phase portrait)\")\n",
        "ax.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "ax.legend(fontsize=9)\n",
        "panel_label(ax, \"e\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# (f) Growth full year (log): xL only\n",
        "ax = axs[5]\n",
        "ax.plot(ab[\"day\"], np.maximum(ab[\"xL\"], eps), label=\"AB xL\")\n",
        "ax.plot(ba[\"day\"], np.maximum(ba[\"xL\"], eps), label=\"BA xL\")\n",
        "ax.set_yscale(\"log\")\n",
        "ax.set_ylim(min_x, max_x)\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Day\"); ax.set_ylabel(\"x (log)\")\n",
        "ax.set_title(\"Growth (log), full year\")\n",
        "ax.grid(True, which=\"both\", linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "ax.legend(fontsize=9)\n",
        "panel_label(ax, \"f\")\n",
        "\n",
        "fig.suptitle(\"Ordering gates chirality expression: AB vs BA under seasonal+diurnal UV (resource-limited)\", y=1.02, fontsize=13)\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "\n",
        "out_png = \"FIG_main_diurnal_AB_vs_BA.png\"\n",
        "plt.savefig(out_png, dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "print(\"Saved:\", out_png)"
      ],

      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "def seasonal_factor(day, period_days=365, amp=0.0, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (day / period_days) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal_factor(step, steps_per_day, amp=0.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (step / steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def simulate_year_world(\n",
        "    days=365,\n",
        "    steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "    x0=0.20,\n",
        "    xmin=0.15,\n",
        "    a=3.0,\n",
        "    b=2.0,\n",
        "    chiral_bias=0.01,\n",
        "    chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        "    K=10.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    uv_phase=0.0,\n",
        "    a_phase=0.0,\n",
        "):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "\n",
        "    aL0 = a * (1.0 + chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"growth\", \"both\") else a\n",
        "    aR0 = a * (1.0 - chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"growth\", \"both\") else a\n",
        "    bL0 = b * (1.0 - chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"damage\", \"both\") else b\n",
        "    bR0 = b * (1.0 + chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"damage\", \"both\") else b\n",
        "\n",
        "    xL = float(x0)\n",
        "    xR = float(x0)\n",
        "\n",
        "    xL_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    xR_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    adv_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    uv_mean_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    uv_peak_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "    a_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        uv_season = seasonal_factor(day, period_days=days, amp=seasonal_uv_amp, phase=uv_phase)\n",
        "        a_mult = seasonal_factor(day, period_days=days, amp=seasonal_a_amp, phase=a_phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "        aL = aL0 * a_mult\n",
        "        aR = aR0 * a_mult\n",
        "\n",
        "        uv_samples = []\n",
        "\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "\n",
        "            uv_inst = uv_season * diurnal_factor(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp)\n",
        "            uv_samples.append(uv_inst)\n",
        "\n",
        "            bL = bL0 * uv_inst\n",
        "            bR = bR0 * uv_inst\n",
        "\n",
        "            if gate == \"A\":\n",
        "                if xL >= xmin and K > 0:\n",
        "                    xL += (aL * xL * (1.0 - xL / K)) * dt\n",
        "                if xR >= xmin and K > 0:\n",
        "                    xR += (aR * xR * (1.0 - xR / K)) * dt\n",
        "            else:\n",
        "                xL -= (bL * xL) * dt\n",
        "                xR -= (bR * xR) * dt\n",
        "\n",
        "            if xL < 0.0: xL = 0.0\n",
        "            if xR < 0.0: xR = 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "        uv_samples = np.array(uv_samples, dtype=float)\n",
        "        uv_mean_daily[day] = float(np.mean(uv_samples))\n",
        "        uv_peak_daily[day] = float(np.max(uv_samples))\n",
        "        a_daily[day] = a_mult\n",
        "\n",
        "        xL_daily[day] = xL\n",
        "        xR_daily[day] = xR\n",
        "        adv_daily[day] = xL - xR\n",
        "\n",
        "    df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "        \"day\": np.arange(days),\n",
        "        \"xL\": xL_daily,\n",
        "        \"xR\": xR_daily,\n",
        "        \"adv\": adv_daily,\n",
        "        \"uv_mean\": uv_mean_daily,\n",
        "        \"uv_peak\": uv_peak_daily,\n",
        "        \"a_mult\": a_daily,\n",
        "    })\n",
        "    return df\n",
        "\n",
        "def summarize_world(df, label, eps=1e-12):\n",
        "    adv = df[\"adv\"].values\n",
        "    xL = df[\"xL\"].values\n",
        "    xR = df[\"xR\"].values\n",
        "\n",
        "    aoi_like = float(np.sum(np.maximum(adv, 0.0)))\n",
        "    peak_adv = float(np.max(adv))\n",
        "    final_adv = float(adv[-1])\n",
        "    final_xL = float(xL[-1])\n",
        "    final_xR = float(xR[-1])\n",
        "\n",
        "    # \"Persistence\": number of days with xL above eps (simple viability proxy)\n",
        "    persistence_days = int(np.sum(xL > eps))\n",
        "\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"world\": label,\n",
        "        \"peak_adv\": peak_adv,\n",
        "        \"aoi_like_sum_pos_adv\": aoi_like,\n",
        "        \"final_xL\": final_xL,\n",
        "        \"final_xR\": final_xR,\n",
        "        \"final_adv\": final_adv,\n",
        "        \"persistence_days_xL>eps\": persistence_days,\n",
        "        \"uv_mean_min\": float(df[\"uv_mean\"].min()),\n",
        "        \"uv_mean_max\": float(df[\"uv_mean\"].max()),\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "def run_four_worlds_and_report(\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "    base_params=None,\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "):\n",
        "    if base_params is None:\n",
        "        base_params = dict(\n",
        "            days=365,\n",
        "            steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "            x0=0.20,\n",
        "            xmin=0.15,\n",
        "            a=3.0,\n",
        "            b=2.0,\n",
        "            chiral_bias=0.01,\n",
        "            chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        "            K=10.0,\n",
        "            seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "        )\n",
        "\n",
        "    worlds = {\n",
        "        \"A_no_diurnal_no_season\": dict(seasonal_uv_amp=0.0, diurnal_uv_amp=0.0),\n",
        "        \"B_diurnal_only\":         dict(seasonal_uv_amp=0.0, diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp),\n",
        "        \"C_season_only\":          dict(seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp, diurnal_uv_amp=0.0),\n",
        "        \"D_diurnal_and_season\":   dict(seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp, diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp),\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "    dfs = {}\n",
        "    summaries = []\n",
        "\n",
        "    for label, w in worlds.items():\n",
        "        df = simulate_year_world(protocol=protocol, **base_params, **w)\n",
        "        dfs[label] = df\n",
        "        summaries.append(summarize_world(df, label))\n",
        "\n",
        "    summary_df = pd.DataFrame(summaries).sort_values(\"world\")\n",
        "    summary_df.to_csv(\"worlds_summary.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "    print(\"Saved: worlds_summary.csv\")\n",
        "    print(summary_df.to_string(index=False))\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Bar-style comparison plots (simple)\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 4))\n",
        "    plt.bar(summary_df[\"world\"], summary_df[\"aoi_like_sum_pos_adv\"])\n",
        "    plt.xticks(rotation=25, ha=\"right\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"AOI-like cumulative advantage (sum adv+)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"World comparison (protocol={protocol})\")\n",
        "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "    plt.savefig(\"worlds_bar_aoi_like.png\", dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "    plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 4))\n",
        "    plt.bar(summary_df[\"world\"], summary_df[\"persistence_days_xL>eps\"])\n",
        "    plt.xticks(rotation=25, ha=\"right\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"Persistence days (xL > eps)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"World comparison (protocol={protocol})\")\n",
        "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "    plt.savefig(\"worlds_bar_persistence.png\", dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "    plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "    return dfs, summary_df\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- RUN IT ---\n",
        "dfs, summary_df = run_four_worlds_and_report(\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",            # try also \"BA\" as a stress-test\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        ")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 774

        "id": "B8q2G68v1lGx",
        "outputId": "72c56664-9e70-4cb8-c0ce-f10010a003d3"

      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {

          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Saved: worlds_summary.csv\n",
            "                 world  peak_adv  aoi_like_sum_pos_adv      final_xL      final_xR     final_adv  persistence_days_xL>eps  uv_mean_min  uv_mean_max\n",
            "A_no_diurnal_no_season  0.210103             60.832497  1.913543e+00  1.746428e+00  1.671151e-01                      365     1.000000     1.000000\n",

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "def seasonal_factor(day, period_days=365, amp=0.6, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (day / period_days) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal_factor(step, steps_per_day, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2.0 * np.pi * (step / steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def make_latitude_uv_factors(num_zones=7, equator_high=1.0, pole_low=0.25, curve=1.5):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Returns lat_uv[z] factors from equator to poles (symmetric).\n",
        "    num_zones should be odd to include an equator band.\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    z = np.arange(num_zones)\n",
        "    mid = (num_zones - 1) / 2.0\n",
        "    dist = np.abs(z - mid) / mid  # 0 at equator, 1 at poles\n",
        "    # smoothly decrease UV toward poles\n",
        "    lat_uv = pole_low + (equator_high - pole_low) * (1.0 - dist**curve)\n",
        "    return lat_uv\n",
        "\n",
        "def simulate_year_spherical(\n",
        "    tag=\"sphere\",\n",
        "    days=365,\n",
        "    steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "    num_zones=7,\n",
        "    mixing_rate=0.03,          # 0 = no mixing; typical 0.01–0.10\n",
        "    shelter_mask=None,         # array len=num_zones, multiplies UV (<=1); if None, all 1\n",
        "    lat_uv=None,               # array len=num_zones; if None, generated\n",
        "    x0=0.20,\n",
        "    xmin=0.15,\n",
        "    a=3.0,\n",
        "    b=2.0,\n",
        "    K=10.0,\n",
        "    chiral_bias=0.01,\n",
        "    chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    uv_phase=0.0,\n",
        "    a_phase=0.0,\n",
        "    save_npz=True,\n",
        "    save_csv=True,\n",
        "):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    State per latitude band: xL[z], xR[z]\n",
        "    UV per band: seasonal * diurnal * lat_uv[z] * shelter_mask[z]\n",
        "    After each day: optional mixing between adjacent latitude bands.\n",
        "    Saves:\n",
        "      - {tag}_zones_timeseries.csv (per-day, per-zone)\n",
        "      - {tag}_aggregate_timeseries.csv (per-day, global sums + advantage)\n",
        "      - {tag}_data.npz (arrays)\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    if lat_uv is None:\n",
        "        lat_uv = make_latitude_uv_factors(num_zones=num_zones, equator_high=1.0, pole_low=0.25, curve=1.5)\n",
        "    lat_uv = np.array(lat_uv, dtype=float)\n",
        "\n",
        "    if shelter_mask is None:\n",
        "        shelter_mask = np.ones(num_zones, dtype=float)\n",
        "    shelter_mask = np.array(shelter_mask, dtype=float)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Chirality modifiers\n",
        "    aL0 = a * (1.0 + chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"growth\", \"both\") else a\n",
        "    aR0 = a * (1.0 - chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"growth\", \"both\") else a\n",
        "    bL0 = b * (1.0 - chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"damage\", \"both\") else b\n",
        "    bR0 = b * (1.0 + chiral_bias) if chirality_in in (\"damage\", \"both\") else b\n",
        "\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Initialise zones\n",
        "    xL = np.full(num_zones, float(x0))\n",
        "    xR = np.full(num_zones, float(x0))\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Logs\n",
        "    xL_daily = np.zeros((days, num_zones))\n",
        "    xR_daily = np.zeros((days, num_zones))\n",
        "    adv_daily = np.zeros((days, num_zones))\n",
        "    uv_mean_daily = np.zeros((days, num_zones))\n",
        "    uv_peak_daily = np.zeros((days, num_zones))\n",
        "    a_daily = np.zeros(days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        uv_season = seasonal_factor(day, period_days=days, amp=seasonal_uv_amp, phase=uv_phase)\n",
        "        a_mult    = seasonal_factor(day, period_days=days, amp=seasonal_a_amp, phase=a_phase)\n",
        "        a_daily[day] = a_mult\n",
        "\n",
        "        aL = aL0 * a_mult\n",
        "        aR = aR0 * a_mult\n",
        "\n",
        "        # track UV samples per zone\n",
        "        uv_samples = np.zeros((steps_per_day, num_zones), dtype=float)\n",
        "\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "\n",
        "            uv_diurnal = diurnal_factor(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp)\n",
        "            uv_inst_zone = uv_season * uv_diurnal * lat_uv * shelter_mask\n",
        "            uv_samples[step, :] = uv_inst_zone\n",
        "\n",
        "            bL_zone = bL0 * uv_inst_zone\n",
        "            bR_zone = bR0 * uv_inst_zone\n",
        "\n",
        "            if gate == \"A\":\n",
        "                # logistic (resource-limited) growth if admissible\n",
        "                growL = (xL >= xmin) & (K > 0)\n",
        "                growR = (xR >= xmin) & (K > 0)\n",
        "                xL[growL] += (aL * xL[growL] * (1.0 - xL[growL] / K)) * dt\n",
        "                xR[growR] += (aR * xR[growR] * (1.0 - xR[growR] / K)) * dt\n",
        "            else:\n",
        "                xL -= (bL_zone * xL) * dt\n",
        "                xR -= (bR_zone * xR) * dt\n",
        "\n",
        "            xL = np.maximum(xL, 0.0)\n",
        "            xR = np.maximum(xR, 0.0)\n",
        "\n",
        "        # After the day: mix between zones (simple 1D diffusion on latitude bands)\n",
        "        if mixing_rate > 0:\n",
        "            m = float(mixing_rate)\n",
        "            xL_new = xL.copy()\n",
        "            xR_new = xR.copy()\n",
        "            for z in range(num_zones):\n",
        "                if z > 0:\n",
        "                    xL_new[z] += m * (xL[z-1] - xL[z])\n",
        "                    xR_new[z] += m * (xR[z-1] - xR[z])\n",
        "                if z < num_zones - 1:\n",
        "                    xL_new[z] += m * (xL[z+1] - xL[z])\n",
        "                    xR_new[z] += m * (xR[z+1] - xR[z])\n",
        "            xL = np.maximum(xL_new, 0.0)\n",
        "            xR = np.maximum(xR_new, 0.0)\n",
        "\n",
        "        xL_daily[day, :] = xL\n",
        "        xR_daily[day, :] = xR\n",
        "        adv_daily[day, :] = xL - xR\n",
        "        uv_mean_daily[day, :] = uv_samples.mean(axis=0)\n",
        "        uv_peak_daily[day, :] = uv_samples.max(axis=0)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Save per-zone CSV (long format)\n",
        "    if save_csv:\n",
        "        rows = []\n",
        "        for day in range(days):\n",
        "            for z in range(num_zones):\n",
        "                rows.append({\n",
        "                    \"tag\": tag,\n",
        "                    \"day\": day,\n",
        "                    \"zone\": z,\n",
        "                    \"lat_uv\": float(lat_uv[z]),\n",
        "                    \"shelter\": float(shelter_mask[z]),\n",
        "                    \"xL\": float(xL_daily[day, z]),\n",
        "                    \"xR\": float(xR_daily[day, z]),\n",
        "                    \"adv\": float(adv_daily[day, z]),\n",
        "                    \"uv_mean\": float(uv_mean_daily[day, z]),\n",
        "                    \"uv_peak\": float(uv_peak_daily[day, z]),\n",
        "                    \"a_mult\": float(a_daily[day]),\n",
        "                })\n",
        "        zones_df = pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "        zones_df.to_csv(f\"{tag}_zones_timeseries.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "        # Aggregate CSV (sums over zones)\n",
        "        agg = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "            \"tag\": tag,\n",
        "            \"day\": np.arange(days),\n",
        "            \"xL_sum\": xL_daily.sum(axis=1),\n",
        "            \"xR_sum\": xR_daily.sum(axis=1),\n",
        "            \"adv_sum\": adv_daily.sum(axis=1),\n",
        "            \"uv_mean_global\": uv_mean_daily.mean(axis=1),\n",
        "            \"uv_peak_global\": uv_peak_daily.max(axis=1),\n",
        "            \"a_mult\": a_daily,\n",
        "        })\n",
        "        agg.to_csv(f\"{tag}_aggregate_timeseries.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Save NPZ\n",
        "    if save_npz:\n",
        "        np.savez(\n",
        "            f\"{tag}_data.npz\",\n",
        "            xL_daily=xL_daily, xR_daily=xR_daily, adv_daily=adv_daily,\n",
        "            uv_mean_daily=uv_mean_daily, uv_peak_daily=uv_peak_daily,\n",
        "            a_daily=a_daily, lat_uv=lat_uv, shelter_mask=shelter_mask\n",
        "        )\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Saved:\",\n",
        "          f\"{tag}_zones_timeseries.csv, {tag}_aggregate_timeseries.csv, {tag}_data.npz\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"tag\": tag,\n",
        "        \"lat_uv\": lat_uv,\n",
        "        \"shelter_mask\": shelter_mask,\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "# ----------------------------\n",
        "# RUN TWO SCENARIOS\n",
        "# ----------------------------\n",
        "num_zones = 7\n",
        "lat_uv = make_latitude_uv_factors(num_zones=num_zones, equator_high=1.0, pole_low=0.25, curve=1.5)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Scenario 1: \"Bare sphere\" (no shelter), mild mixing\n",
        "shelter_none = np.ones(num_zones)\n",
        "\n",
        "simulate_year_spherical(\n",
        "    tag=\"sphere_bare\",\n",
        "    num_zones=num_zones,\n",
        "    lat_uv=lat_uv,\n",
        "    shelter_mask=shelter_none,\n",
        "    mixing_rate=0.03,\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    x0=0.20, xmin=0.15, a=3.0, b=2.0, K=10.0,\n",
        "    chiral_bias=0.01, chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Scenario 2: Add a \"refuge\" (shade/shelter) at the poles + some mid-lat shelter\n",
        "# Example: poles are heavily shielded, mid-lats partially shielded, equator exposed\n",
        "shelter_refuge = np.ones(num_zones)\n",
        "shelter_refuge[0] = 0.15   # pole\n",
        "shelter_refuge[-1] = 0.15  # pole\n",
        "shelter_refuge[1] = 0.50\n",
        "shelter_refuge[-2] = 0.50\n",
        "\n",
        "simulate_year_spherical(\n",
        "    tag=\"sphere_refuge\",\n",
        "    num_zones=num_zones,\n",
        "    lat_uv=lat_uv,\n",
        "    shelter_mask=shelter_refuge,\n",
        "    mixing_rate=0.03,\n",
        "    protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "    seasonal_uv_amp=0.6,\n",
        "    diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "    seasonal_a_amp=0.0,\n",
        "    x0=0.20, xmin=0.15, a=3.0, b=2.0, K=10.0,\n",
        "    chiral_bias=0.01, chirality_in=\"both\",\n",
        ")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "G_V2cRom5A8u",
        "outputId": "1b023efe-7679-4e54-b80f-214417e225c2"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [

            "Saved: sphere_refuge_zones_timeseries.csv, sphere_refuge_aggregate_timeseries.csv, sphere_refuge_data.npz\n"

              " 'lat_uv': array([0.25      , 0.59175171, 0.85566243, 1.        , 0.85566243,\n",
              "        0.59175171, 0.25      ]),\n",
              " 'shelter_mask': array([0.15, 0.5 , 1.  , 1.  , 1.  , 0.5 , 0.15])}"
            ]

          "metadata": {},

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "OUTDIR = \"figs_sphere\"\n",
        "os.makedirs(OUTDIR, exist_ok=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "def load_npz(tag):\n",
        "    return np.load(f\"{tag}_data.npz\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def load_agg(tag):\n",
        "    return pd.read_csv(f\"{tag}_aggregate_timeseries.csv\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def savefig(name):\n",
        "    path = os.path.join(OUTDIR, f\"{name}.png\")\n",
        "    plt.savefig(path, dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "    print(\"Saved:\", path)\n",
        "\n",
        "def plot_global(tag1, tag2):\n",
        "    a1 = load_agg(tag1)\n",
        "    a2 = load_agg(tag2)\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
        "    plt.plot(a1[\"day\"], a1[\"xL_sum\"], label=f\"{tag1} xL_sum\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(a1[\"day\"], a1[\"xR_sum\"], linestyle=\"--\", label=f\"{tag1} xR_sum\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(a2[\"day\"], a2[\"xL_sum\"], label=f\"{tag2} xL_sum\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(a2[\"day\"], a2[\"xR_sum\"], linestyle=\"--\", label=f\"{tag2} xR_sum\")\n",
        "    plt.yscale(\"log\")\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Day\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"Global x (log)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(\"Global growth (sum over latitude bands)\")\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, which=\"both\", linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend(fontsize=8)\n",
        "    savefig(\"Fig1_global_growth_log\")\n",
        "    plt.close()\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 3.6))\n",
        "    plt.plot(a1[\"day\"], a1[\"adv_sum\"], label=f\"{tag1} adv_sum\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(a2[\"day\"], a2[\"adv_sum\"], label=f\"{tag2} adv_sum\")\n",
        "    plt.axhline(0, linewidth=0.7)\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Day\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"Global advantage (sum)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(\"Global advantage (chirality expression)\")\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend()\n",
        "    savefig(\"Fig1b_global_adv\")\n",
        "    plt.close()\n",
        "\n",
        "def plot_uv_context(tag):\n",
        "    a = load_agg(tag)\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 3.6))\n",
        "    plt.plot(a[\"day\"], a[\"uv_mean_global\"], label=\"UV mean (global)\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(a[\"day\"], a[\"uv_peak_global\"], linestyle=\"--\", label=\"UV peak (global)\")\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Day\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"UV\")\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"UV forcing (global) — {tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend()\n",
        "    savefig(f\"Fig2_uv_{tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.close()\n",
        "\n",
        "def heatmap_xL(tag, title):\n",
        "    d = load_npz(tag)\n",
        "    xL = d[\"xL_daily\"]  # shape (days, zones)\n",
        "    lat_uv = d[\"lat_uv\"]\n",
        "    shelter = d[\"shelter_mask\"]\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Plot log10(xL + eps)\n",
        "    eps = 1e-12\n",
        "    Z = np.log10(xL + eps).T  # zones x days\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
        "    plt.imshow(Z, aspect=\"auto\", origin=\"lower\")\n",
        "    plt.colorbar(label=\"log10(xL + eps)\")\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Day\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"Latitude band (0=pole … mid=equator … last=pole)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(title)\n",
        "    savefig(f\"Fig3_heatmap_{tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.close()\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Also save a small table of zone factors for reference\n",
        "    zone_df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "        \"zone\": np.arange(len(lat_uv)),\n",
        "        \"lat_uv_factor\": lat_uv,\n",
        "        \"shelter_factor\": shelter\n",
        "    })\n",
        "    zone_df.to_csv(os.path.join(OUTDIR, f\"{tag}_zone_factors.csv\"), index=False)\n",
        "    print(\"Saved:\", os.path.join(OUTDIR, f\"{tag}_zone_factors.csv\"))\n",
        "\n",
        "def latitude_profiles(tag, days_to_show=(10, 60, 120, 240, 364)):\n",
        "    d = load_npz(tag)\n",
        "    xL = d[\"xL_daily\"]\n",
        "    lat_uv = d[\"lat_uv\"]\n",
        "    shelter = d[\"shelter_mask\"]\n",
        "    zones = np.arange(xL.shape[1])\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
        "    for day in days_to_show:\n",
        "        plt.plot(zones, xL[day, :], label=f\"day {day}\")\n",
        "    plt.yscale(\"log\")\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Zone (0 pole … mid equator … last pole)\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"xL (log)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"Latitude profiles of xL — {tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, which=\"both\", linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend(fontsize=8)\n",
        "    savefig(f\"Fig4_lat_profiles_{tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.close()\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 3))\n",
        "    plt.plot(zones, lat_uv, label=\"lat_uv_factor\")\n",
        "    plt.plot(zones, shelter, linestyle=\"--\", label=\"shelter_factor\")\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Zone\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"Factor\")\n",
        "    plt.title(f\"Latitude UV and shelter factors — {tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.grid(True, linestyle=\":\", linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "    plt.legend()\n",
        "    savefig(f\"Fig4b_lat_factors_{tag}\")\n",
        "    plt.close()\n",
        "\n",
        "# ---- Make the figures ----\n",
        "plot_global(\"sphere_bare\", \"sphere_refuge\")\n",
        "plot_uv_context(\"sphere_bare\")\n",
        "plot_uv_context(\"sphere_refuge\")\n",
        "heatmap_xL(\"sphere_bare\", \"Latitude–time heatmap of xL (bare sphere)\")\n",
        "heatmap_xL(\"sphere_refuge\", \"Latitude–time heatmap of xL (with polar refuge)\")\n",
        "latitude_profiles(\"sphere_bare\")\n",
        "latitude_profiles(\"sphere_refuge\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Done. Figures saved to:\", OUTDIR)"
      ],

      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import math\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import matplotlib.image as mpimg\n",
        "\n",
        "FIGDIR = \"figs_sphere\"\n",
        "OUTPNG = os.path.join(FIGDIR, \"PANEL_spherical_world.png\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Collect all PNGs\n",
        "pngs = [f for f in os.listdir(FIGDIR) if f.lower().endswith(\".png\")]\n",
        "if not pngs:\n",
        "    raise FileNotFoundError(f\"No PNG files found in {FIGDIR}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Heuristic ordering for readability ---\n",
        "def score(name):\n",
        "    n = name.lower()\n",
        "    s = 100\n",
        "    if \"global\" in n: s = 0\n",
        "    elif \"uv\" in n: s = 1\n",
        "    elif \"heatmap\" in n: s = 2\n",
        "    elif \"lat\" in n or \"latitude\" in n: s = 3\n",
        "    elif \"adv\" in n: s = 4\n",
        "    elif \"growth\" in n: s = 5\n",
        "    return s\n",
        "\n",
        "pngs.sort(key=score)\n",
        "\n",
        "paths = [os.path.join(FIGDIR, f) for f in pngs]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Panel order:\")\n",
        "for i, p in enumerate(paths):\n",
        "    print(f\"{i+1:02d}  {os.path.basename(p)}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Panel geometry ---\n",
        "n = len(paths)\n",
        "cols = 3 if n >= 6 else 2\n",
        "rows = math.ceil(n / cols)\n",
        "\n",
        "fig_w = 6.0 * cols\n",
        "fig_h = 3.8 * rows\n",
        "\n",
        "fig, axes = plt.subplots(rows, cols, figsize=(fig_w, fig_h))\n",
        "axes = axes.flatten() if hasattr(axes, \"flatten\") else [axes]\n",
        "\n",
        "for ax in axes:\n",
        "    ax.axis(\"off\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Render images ---\n",
        "for i, path in enumerate(paths):\n",
        "    img = mpimg.imread(path)\n",
        "    axes[i].imshow(img)\n",
        "    axes[i].set_title(os.path.basename(path), fontsize=8)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.savefig(OUTPNG, dpi=300, bbox_inches=\"tight\")\n",
        "plt.close(fig)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\nSaved compiled panel:\", OUTPNG)"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Environment gates\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period=365, amp=0.0, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(day/period) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=0.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(step/steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gates_for_step(day, step, steps_per_day, *,\n",
        "                   seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                   seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                   refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Two primitive gates:\n",
        "      wet(t): assembly/solvation/access window\n",
        "      uv(t):  damage or activation window (depending on edge)\n",
        "    refuge <1 reduces UV (shelter).\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    uv = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2)  # optional wet season (90° shifted)\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Tiny contender graphs\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Each graph: nodes list, edges list\n",
        "# Edge = (src, dst, base_k, gate_type, direction)\n",
        "# gate_type: \"wet\", \"uv\", or \"none\"\n",
        "# direction: +1 means production, -1 means degradation of dst (we implement as loss on dst)\n",
        "\n",
        "FAD_GRAPH = {\n",
        "    \"name\": \"FAD\",\n",
        "    \"nodes\": [\"Ribo\", \"FMN\", \"FAD\"],\n",
        "    \"edges\": [\n",
        "        (\"Ribo\", \"FMN\",  0.10, \"wet\",  +1),   # phosphorylation proxy (wet/chem access)\n",
        "        (\"FMN\",  \"FAD\",  0.06, \"wet\",  +1),   # adenylation proxy (wet/chem access)\n",
        "        (\"FMN\",  \"FMN\",  0.02, \"uv\",   -1),   # UV damage of intermediate\n",
        "        (\"FAD\",  \"FAD\",  0.01, \"uv\",   -1),   # UV damage of product\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    \"seed\": {\"Ribo\": 1.0},\n",
        "    \"target\": \"FAD\",\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "NAD_GRAPH = {\n",
        "    \"name\": \"NAD\",\n",
        "    \"nodes\": [\"Prec\", \"NR\", \"NAD\"],\n",
        "    \"edges\": [\n",
        "        (\"Prec\", \"NR\",   0.08, \"wet\", +1),    # precursor -> nicotinamide riboside proxy\n",
        "        (\"NR\",   \"NAD\",  0.05, \"uv\",  +1),    # light-activated step (per 2024 NAD paper)\n",
        "        (\"NR\",   \"NR\",   0.02, \"uv\",  -1),    # UV damage of intermediate\n",
        "        (\"NAD\",  \"NAD\",  0.01, \"uv\",  -1),    # UV damage of product\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    \"seed\": {\"Prec\": 1.0},\n",
        "    \"target\": \"NAD\",\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "THIO_GRAPH = {\n",
        "    \"name\": \"Thioester\",\n",
        "    \"nodes\": [\"Acid\", \"Thio\", \"Work\"],\n",
        "    \"edges\": [\n",
        "        (\"Acid\", \"Thio\", 0.07, \"wet\", +1),    # thioester formation proxy (wet/catalysis)\n",
        "        (\"Thio\", \"Work\", 0.05, \"wet\", +1),    # energy coupling into useful work pool\n",
        "        (\"Thio\", \"Thio\", 0.03, \"uv\",  -1),    # thioester hydrolysis/photodamage proxy\n",
        "        (\"Work\", \"Work\", 0.01, \"uv\",  -1),    # UV destroys accumulated work\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    \"seed\": {\"Acid\": 1.0},\n",
        "    \"target\": \"Work\",  # treat usable energy/coupling as target\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "CONTENDERS = [FAD_GRAPH, NAD_GRAPH, THIO_GRAPH]\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Simulation engine (AOI-style ordering AB vs BA)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def run_graph(graph, *, days=365, steps_per_day=200, protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0, seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "              refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    nodes = graph[\"nodes\"]\n",
        "    idx = {n:i for i,n in enumerate(nodes)}\n",
        "    x = np.zeros(len(nodes), dtype=float)\n",
        "\n",
        "    for k,v in graph[\"seed\"].items():\n",
        "        x[idx[k]] = float(v)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # store target over days\n",
        "    target = graph[\"target\"]\n",
        "    t_idx = idx[target]\n",
        "    target_daily = np.zeros(days, dtype=float)\n",
        "\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            gateA, gateUV = gates_for_step(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                                           seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                           diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                           seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                                           refuge=refuge)\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "            wet_on = 1.0 if gate == \"A\" else 0.0\n",
        "            uv_on  = 1.0 if gate == \"B\" else 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "            # effective gate values this step\n",
        "            wet = wet_on * gateA\n",
        "            uv  = uv_on  * gateUV\n",
        "\n",
        "            # apply edges (simple mass-action-ish)\n",
        "            for (src, dst, k0, gate_type, direction) in graph[\"edges\"]:\n",
        "                j_src = idx[src]\n",
        "                j_dst = idx[dst]\n",
        "                g = 1.0\n",
        "                if gate_type == \"wet\":\n",
        "                    g = wet\n",
        "                elif gate_type == \"uv\":\n",
        "                    g = uv\n",
        "\n",
        "                if direction > 0:\n",
        "                    # production flow from src to dst (src consumed proportionally)\n",
        "                    flow = k0 * g * x[j_src] * dt\n",
        "                    x[j_src] = max(0.0, x[j_src] - flow)\n",
        "                    x[j_dst] += flow\n",
        "                else:\n",
        "                    # degradation on dst\n",
        "                    loss = k0 * g * x[j_dst] * dt\n",
        "                    x[j_dst] = max(0.0, x[j_dst] - loss)\n",
        "\n",
        "        target_daily[day] = x[t_idx]\n",
        "\n",
        "    return target_daily\n",
        "\n",
        "def score_series(series):\n",
        "    # simple AOI-like scoring: final + cumulative (weights adjustable)\n",
        "    final = float(series[-1])\n",
        "    cumulative = float(np.sum(series))\n",
        "    return final, cumulative\n",
        "\n",
        "def tournament(env_label, env_kwargs):\n",
        "    rows = []\n",
        "    for g in CONTENDERS:\n",
        "        ab = run_graph(g, protocol=\"AB\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "        ba = run_graph(g, protocol=\"BA\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "        ab_final, ab_cum = score_series(ab)\n",
        "        ba_final, ba_cum = score_series(ba)\n",
        "        rows.append({\n",
        "            \"env\": env_label,\n",
        "            \"contender\": g[\"name\"],\n",
        "            \"AB_final\": ab_final,\n",
        "            \"BA_final\": ba_final,\n",
        "            \"AB_cum\": ab_cum,\n",
        "            \"BA_cum\": ba_cum,\n",
        "            \"AOI_gap_final\": ab_final - ba_final,\n",
        "            \"AOI_gap_cum\": ab_cum - ba_cum,\n",
        "        })\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Run a small environment set\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "envs = {\n",
        "    # exposed equator\n",
        "    \"equator_exposed\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                            refuge=1.0),\n",
        "    # sheltered/refuge (UV suppressed)\n",
        "    \"refuge_sheltered\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                             seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                             seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                             refuge=0.3),\n",
        "    # add wet season (resource/assembly seasonality)\n",
        "    \"wet_season_refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                              seasonal_wet_amp=0.6,\n",
        "                              refuge=0.3),\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "all_df = pd.concat([tournament(name, kwargs) for name,kwargs in envs.items()], ignore_index=True)\n",
        "all_df.to_csv(\"AOI_tournament_optionA.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(all_df.sort_values([\"env\", \"AOI_gap_cum\"], ascending=[True, False]).to_string(index=False))\n",
        "print(\"\\nSaved: AOI_tournament_optionA.csv\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "jbtEZw4zFAja",
        "outputId": "4726d977-7d08-4c2d-f5b3-49925e73c1f8"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "              env contender  AB_final  BA_final     AB_cum     BA_cum  AOI_gap_final  AOI_gap_cum\n",
            "  equator_exposed       NAD  0.155874  0.162057  98.466422  99.852512      -0.006183    -1.386091\n",
            "  equator_exposed Thioester  0.124115  0.129714  75.489942  77.615080      -0.005599    -2.125137\n",
            "  equator_exposed       FAD  0.146169  0.152529  94.963804  97.431543      -0.006359    -2.467739\n",
            " refuge_sheltered       NAD  0.476089  0.479902 152.276788 151.869598      -0.003813     0.407190\n",
            " refuge_sheltered Thioester  0.520105  0.527485 187.800891 189.688743      -0.007380    -1.887852\n",
            " refuge_sheltered       FAD  0.557745  0.565038 211.719671 213.614890      -0.007294    -1.895219\n",
            "wet_season_refuge       NAD  0.471010  0.475105 155.898336 155.578072      -0.004096     0.320264\n",
            "wet_season_refuge Thioester  0.530406  0.537698 206.880108 208.801630      -0.007292    -1.921522\n",
            "wet_season_refuge       FAD  0.561624  0.568870 227.674999 229.608294      -0.007246    -1.933295\n",
            "\n",
            "Saved: AOI_tournament_optionA.csv\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Environment gates\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period=365, amp=0.0, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(day/period) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=0.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(step/steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gates_for_step(day, step, steps_per_day, *,\n",
        "                   seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                   seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                   refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    uv = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2)  # optional wet season\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Contender graphs\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Edge = (src, dst, base_k, gate_type, direction)\n",
        "# gate_type: \"wet\", \"uv\", or \"none\"\n",
        "# direction: +1 production flow src->dst, -1 degradation on dst\n",
        "#\n",
        "# NEW: graphs may include \"modifiers\" to warp wet/uv gates based on internal state.\n",
        "\n",
        "FAD_PLUS = {\n",
        "    \"name\": \"FAD_PLUS\",\n",
        "    \"nodes\": [\"Ribo\", \"FMN\", \"FAD\", \"FADH2\", \"Shield\", \"Waste\"],\n",
        "    \"edges\": [\n",
        "        # (5) Recycling / findability: Waste -> Ribo under wet\n",
        "        (\"Waste\", \"Ribo\", 0.03, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "\n",
        "        # Core lineage (riboflavin -> FMN -> FAD), wet-gated\n",
        "        (\"Ribo\", \"FMN\",   0.10, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "        (\"FMN\",  \"FAD\",   0.06, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "\n",
        "        # (1) Battery / redox state: charge under wet, discharge under UV\n",
        "        (\"FAD\",   \"FADH2\", 0.05, \"wet\", +1),  # reduction/charging\n",
        "        (\"FADH2\", \"FAD\",   0.05, \"uv\",  +1),  # oxidation/discharging\n",
        "\n",
        "        # (4) Shelter accretion proxy: Shield produced from FAD under wet\n",
        "        (\"FAD\", \"Shield\", 0.02, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "\n",
        "        # Degradation under UV (2): FADH2 more UV-robust than FAD\n",
        "        (\"FMN\",   \"Waste\", 0.02, \"uv\", +1),   # intermediate loss\n",
        "        (\"FAD\",   \"Waste\", 0.02, \"uv\", +1),   # product loss (higher)\n",
        "        (\"FADH2\", \"Waste\", 0.005,\"uv\", +1),   # reduced form loss (lower)\n",
        "        (\"Shield\",\"Waste\", 0.002,\"uv\", +1),   # shield decays slowly\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    \"seed\": {\"Ribo\": 1.0},\n",
        "    \"target\": \"FAD\",  # we score total flavin pool too (see below)\n",
        "    \"modifiers\": {\n",
        "        # (3) Catalytic bootstrapping: wet gate amplified by FAD pool\n",
        "        \"wet_boost_node\": \"FAD\",          # node that boosts wet accessibility\n",
        "        \"wet_boost_strength\": 1.5,        # multiplier slope\n",
        "\n",
        "        # (4) Shield reduces effective UV gate\n",
        "        \"uv_shield_node\": \"Shield\",\n",
        "        \"uv_shield_strength\": 0.7,        # fraction of UV suppressed per unit Shield (clipped)\n",
        "\n",
        "        # also score \"total flavin\" as FAD + FADH2 (battery inclusive)\n",
        "        \"score_total_nodes\": [\"FAD\", \"FADH2\"],\n",
        "    }\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "NAD_GRAPH = {\n",
        "    \"name\": \"NAD\",\n",
        "    \"nodes\": [\"Prec\", \"NR\", \"NAD\", \"Waste\"],\n",
        "    \"edges\": [\n",
        "        (\"Prec\", \"NR\",   0.08, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "        (\"NR\",   \"NAD\",  0.05, \"uv\",  +1),   # UV-activated step\n",
        "        (\"NR\",   \"Waste\",0.02, \"uv\",  +1),\n",
        "        (\"NAD\",  \"Waste\",0.01, \"uv\",  +1),\n",
        "        (\"Waste\",\"Prec\", 0.01, \"wet\", +1),  # mild recycling for fairness\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    \"seed\": {\"Prec\": 1.0},\n",
        "    \"target\": \"NAD\",\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "THIO_GRAPH = {\n",
        "    \"name\": \"Thioester\",\n",
        "    \"nodes\": [\"Acid\", \"Thio\", \"Work\", \"Waste\"],\n",
        "    \"edges\": [\n",
        "        (\"Acid\", \"Thio\", 0.07, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "        (\"Thio\", \"Work\", 0.05, \"wet\", +1),\n",
        "        (\"Thio\", \"Waste\",0.03, \"uv\",  +1),\n",
        "        (\"Work\", \"Waste\",0.01, \"uv\",  +1),\n",
        "        (\"Waste\",\"Acid\", 0.01, \"wet\", +1),  # mild recycling\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    \"seed\": {\"Acid\": 1.0},\n",
        "    \"target\": \"Work\",\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "CONTENDERS = [NAD_GRAPH, THIO_GRAPH, FAD_PLUS]\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Simulation engine (AOI ordering AB vs BA)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def run_graph(graph, *, days=365, steps_per_day=200, protocol=\"AB\",\n",
        "              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0, seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "              refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    nodes = graph[\"nodes\"]\n",
        "    idx = {n:i for i,n in enumerate(nodes)}\n",
        "    x = np.zeros(len(nodes), dtype=float)\n",
        "    for k,v in graph[\"seed\"].items():\n",
        "        x[idx[k]] = float(v)\n",
        "\n",
        "    mods = graph.get(\"modifiers\", {})\n",
        "    wet_boost_node = mods.get(\"wet_boost_node\", None)\n",
        "    wet_boost_strength = float(mods.get(\"wet_boost_strength\", 0.0))\n",
        "    uv_shield_node = mods.get(\"uv_shield_node\", None)\n",
        "    uv_shield_strength = float(mods.get(\"uv_shield_strength\", 0.0))\n",
        "    score_total_nodes = mods.get(\"score_total_nodes\", None)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Target tracking\n",
        "    if score_total_nodes:\n",
        "        score_idx = [idx[n] for n in score_total_nodes]\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        score_idx = [idx[graph[\"target\"]]]\n",
        "\n",
        "    target_daily = np.zeros(days, dtype=float)\n",
        "\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            gateA, gateUV = gates_for_step(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                                           seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                           diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                           seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                                           refuge=refuge)\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "            wet_on = 1.0 if gate == \"A\" else 0.0\n",
        "            uv_on  = 1.0 if gate == \"B\" else 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "            wet = wet_on * gateA\n",
        "            uv  = uv_on  * gateUV\n",
        "\n",
        "            # (3) Catalytic bootstrapping: wet gate boosted by presence of wet_boost_node\n",
        "            if wet_boost_node is not None and wet > 0:\n",
        "                boost = 1.0 + wet_boost_strength * x[idx[wet_boost_node]]\n",
        "                wet = wet * boost\n",
        "\n",
        "            # (4) Shield reduces UV gate\n",
        "            if uv_shield_node is not None and uv > 0:\n",
        "                shield = x[idx[uv_shield_node]]\n",
        "                uv = uv * max(0.0, 1.0 - uv_shield_strength * shield)\n",
        "\n",
        "            # Apply edges\n",
        "            for (src, dst, k0, gate_type, direction) in graph[\"edges\"]:\n",
        "                j_src = idx[src]\n",
        "                j_dst = idx[dst]\n",
        "\n",
        "                if gate_type == \"wet\":\n",
        "                    g = wet\n",
        "                elif gate_type == \"uv\":\n",
        "                    g = uv\n",
        "                else:\n",
        "                    g = 1.0\n",
        "\n",
        "                if g <= 0:\n",
        "                    continue\n",
        "\n",
        "                if direction > 0:\n",
        "                    flow = k0 * g * x[j_src] * dt\n",
        "                    if flow <= 0:\n",
        "                        continue\n",
        "                    x[j_src] = max(0.0, x[j_src] - flow)\n",
        "                    x[j_dst] += flow\n",
        "                else:\n",
        "                    loss = k0 * g * x[j_dst] * dt\n",
        "                    if loss <= 0:\n",
        "                        continue\n",
        "                    x[j_dst] = max(0.0, x[j_dst] - loss)\n",
        "\n",
        "        target_daily[day] = float(np.sum(x[score_idx]))\n",
        "\n",
        "    return target_daily\n",
        "\n",
        "def score_series(series):\n",
        "    final = float(series[-1])\n",
        "    cumulative = float(np.sum(series))\n",
        "    return final, cumulative\n",
        "\n",
        "def tournament(env_label, env_kwargs):\n",
        "    rows = []\n",
        "    for g in CONTENDERS:\n",
        "        ab = run_graph(g, protocol=\"AB\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "        ba = run_graph(g, protocol=\"BA\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "        ab_final, ab_cum = score_series(ab)\n",
        "        ba_final, ba_cum = score_series(ba)\n",
        "        rows.append({\n",
        "            \"env\": env_label,\n",
        "            \"contender\": g[\"name\"],\n",
        "            \"AB_final\": ab_final,\n",
        "            \"BA_final\": ba_final,\n",
        "            \"AB_cum\": ab_cum,\n",
        "            \"BA_cum\": ba_cum,\n",
        "            \"AOI_gap_final\": ab_final - ba_final,\n",
        "            \"AOI_gap_cum\": ab_cum - ba_cum,\n",
        "        })\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Environments\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "envs = {\n",
        "    \"equator_exposed\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                            refuge=1.0),\n",
        "    \"refuge_sheltered\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                             seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                             seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                             refuge=0.3),\n",
        "    \"wet_season_refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                              seasonal_wet_amp=0.6,\n",
        "                              refuge=0.3),\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "all_df = pd.concat([tournament(name, kwargs) for name, kwargs in envs.items()], ignore_index=True)\n",
        "all_df.to_csv(\"AOI_tournament_optionA_FADPLUS.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(all_df.sort_values([\"env\", \"AOI_gap_cum\"], ascending=[True, False]).to_string(index=False))\n",
        "print(\"\\nSaved: AOI_tournament_optionA_FADPLUS.csv\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {

            "  equator_exposed  FAD_PLUS  0.335617  0.338025 117.145779 118.882765      -0.002408    -1.736985\n",
            "  equator_exposed Thioester  0.424126  0.431490 117.634266 120.055684      -0.007365    -2.421418\n",
            " refuge_sheltered       NAD  0.595015  0.595735 166.739440 165.874684      -0.000720     0.864757\n",

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from collections import defaultdict, deque\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Gates (you can swap in your spherical world UV/wet models later)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period=365, amp=0.6, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(day/period) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(step/steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day, seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0, seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    # UV varies; wet can be constant or seasonal-shifted\n",
        "    uv = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2)\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# FAD graph (minimal backbone + optional upstream precursor nodes)\n",
        "# Each edge has: type (\"wet\"/\"uv\"/\"none\") and baseline k\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Canonical: Riboflavin -> FMN -> FAD (wet-gated) 2\n",
        "# Optional upstream: Start -> Riboflavin (placeholder for riboflavin biosynthesis module) 3\n",
        "\n",
        "EDGES = [\n",
        "    (\"Start\", \"Riboflavin\", \"wet\", 0.08),\n",
        "    (\"Riboflavin\", \"FMN\", \"wet\", 0.10),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\", \"FAD\", \"wet\", 0.06),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Optional: UV damage edges (route penalties)\n",
        "    (\"Riboflavin\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.02),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.02),\n",
        "    (\"FAD\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.01),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Build adjacency for route enumeration (only forward synthesis edges to FAD)\n",
        "SYNTH_EDGES = [(u,v,typ,k) for (u,v,typ,k) in EDGES if v in (\"Riboflavin\",\"FMN\",\"FAD\")]\n",
        "\n",
        "adj = defaultdict(list)\n",
        "edge_info = {}\n",
        "for u,v,typ,k in SYNTH_EDGES:\n",
        "    adj[u].append(v)\n",
        "    edge_info[(u,v)] = (typ,k)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Enumerate simple paths Start -> FAD\n",
        "def enumerate_paths(start=\"Start\", goal=\"FAD\", max_len=10):\n",
        "    paths = []\n",
        "    stack = [(start, [start])]\n",
        "    while stack:\n",
        "        node, path = stack.pop()\n",
        "        if node == goal:\n",
        "            paths.append(path)\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        if len(path) >= max_len:\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        for nxt in adj.get(node, []):\n",
        "            if nxt in path:\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "            stack.append((nxt, path + [nxt]))\n",
        "    return paths\n",
        "\n",
        "paths = enumerate_paths()\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# AOI scoring\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def route_edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                       seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                       seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Compute W_e = sum_t k_e * gate_e(t) * dt for each synthesis edge.\n",
        "    protocol AB vs BA means wet window happens in A half and UV window in B half (or reversed).\n",
        "    Here only synthesis edges are wet-gated, so ordering impacts via wet(t) gating (and later you can add UV-productive steps).\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "\n",
        "    W = {e: 0.0 for e in edge_info.keys()}\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            wet, uv = gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                                  refuge=refuge)\n",
        "\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "            wet_on = 1.0 if gate == \"A\" else 0.0\n",
        "            uv_on  = 1.0 if gate == \"B\" else 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "            wet_eff = wet_on * wet\n",
        "            uv_eff  = uv_on  * uv\n",
        "\n",
        "            for (u,v),(typ,k) in edge_info.items():\n",
        "                g = wet_eff if typ == \"wet\" else (uv_eff if typ == \"uv\" else 1.0)\n",
        "                W[(u,v)] += k * g * dt\n",
        "\n",
        "    return W\n",
        "\n",
        "def path_score(path, W):\n",
        "    # product of edge weights along the path\n",
        "    score = 1.0\n",
        "    for i in range(len(path)-1):\n",
        "        e = (path[i], path[i+1])\n",
        "        score *= W[e]\n",
        "    return score\n",
        "\n",
        "def run_routes(env_label, env_kwargs):\n",
        "    W_AB = route_edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "    W_BA = route_edge_weights(protocol=\"BA\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "\n",
        "    rows = []\n",
        "    for p in paths:\n",
        "        s_ab = path_score(p, W_AB)\n",
        "        s_ba = path_score(p, W_BA)\n",
        "        rows.append({\n",
        "            \"env\": env_label,\n",
        "            \"route\": \" -> \".join(p),\n",
        "            \"S_AB\": s_ab,\n",
        "            \"S_BA\": s_ba,\n",
        "            \"Delta\": s_ab - s_ba,\n",
        "            \"Ratio_AB_over_BA\": (s_ab / s_ba) if s_ba > 0 else np.inf\n",
        "        })\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Example environments\n",
        "envs = {\n",
        "    \"equator_exposed\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200, seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0, seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0),\n",
        "    \"refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200, seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0, seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "    \"wet_season_refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200, seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0, seasonal_wet_amp=0.6, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "all_df = pd.concat([run_routes(name, kwargs) for name,kwargs in envs.items()], ignore_index=True)\n",
        "all_df.to_csv(\"FAD_routes_AOI_scores.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(all_df.sort_values([\"env\",\"Delta\"], ascending=[True, False]).to_string(index=False))\n",
        "print(\"\\nSaved: FAD_routes_AOI_scores.csv\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "xmKQtIUhI84x",
        "outputId": "9ae1123a-0c33-4d72-b6a4-83a2f4329ebf"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [

            "  equator_exposed Start -> Riboflavin -> FMN -> FAD 2917.6275 2917.6275    0.0               1.0\n",
            "           refuge Start -> Riboflavin -> FMN -> FAD 2917.6275 2917.6275    0.0               1.0\n",
            "wet_season_refuge Start -> Riboflavin -> FMN -> FAD 2917.6275 2917.6275    0.0               1.0\n",
            "\n",
            "Saved: FAD_routes_AOI_scores.csv\n"
