    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from collections import defaultdict\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Gates\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period=365, amp=0.0, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(day/period) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(step/steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day, seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    uv  = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2)  # optional wet season\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Build a prebiotic-flavin route graph\n",
        "# Nodes are abstract motifs; edges are candidate transformations\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Edge fields:\n",
        "#   (src, dst, gate_type, k, label)\n",
        "# gate_type in {\"wet\",\"uv\",\"none\"}\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "EDGES = [\n",
        "    # Baseline \"modern-like\" backbone (environment-as-enzyme proxy)\n",
        "    (\"Start\",      \"Riboflavin\", \"wet\", 0.08, \"riboflavin_formation\"),\n",
        "    (\"Riboflavin\", \"FMN\",        \"wet\", 0.10, \"phosphorylation_like\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\",        \"FAD\",        \"wet\", 0.06, \"adenylation_like\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV damage (penalties)\n",
        "    (\"Riboflavin\", \"Waste\",      \"uv\",  0.02, \"uv_damage_ribo\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\",        \"Waste\",      \"uv\",  0.02, \"uv_damage_fmn\"),\n",
        "    (\"FAD\",        \"Waste\",      \"uv\",  0.01, \"uv_damage_fad\"),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# ADD PREBIOTIC AOI-NATIVE EDGES (3+)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# (1) UV-productive step: photochemical activation of riboflavin-like core\n",
        "EDGES += [\n",
        "    (\"Riboflavin\", \"Ribo*\", \"uv\", 0.06, \"photoactivate_ribo\"),\n",
        "    (\"Ribo*\", \"FMN\", \"wet\", 0.14, \"activated_to_fmn_like\"),  # only useful if wet follows UV\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# (2) Wet-protective adsorption: wet puts molecule into a protected state\n",
        "# which is UV-robust, then wet releases back\n",
        "EDGES += [\n",
        "    (\"Riboflavin\", \"AdsRibo\", \"wet\", 0.10, \"adsorb_ribo\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsRibo\", \"Riboflavin\", \"wet\", 0.06, \"desorb_ribo\"),\n",
        "    # UV hits AdsRibo less (smaller k)\n",
        "    (\"AdsRibo\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.002, \"uv_damage_adsorb_low\"),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# (3) Battery/redox intermediate: wet “charges” to a reduced form; UV “discharges” back\n",
        "# plus reduced form is more UV-robust\n",
        "EDGES += [\n",
        "    (\"FAD\", \"FADH2\", \"wet\", 0.08, \"charge_fad\"),\n",
        "    (\"FADH2\", \"FAD\", \"uv\", 0.08, \"discharge_fad\"),\n",
        "    (\"FADH2\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.002, \"uv_damage_fadh2_low\"),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# (4) OPTIONAL: recycling / findability (helps create an ordering backbone)\n",
        "EDGES += [\n",
        "    (\"Waste\", \"Start\", \"wet\", 0.01, \"recycle_pool\"),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Route enumeration (simple paths Start -> FAD)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Only include synthesis-advancing edges for route enumeration\n",
        "SYNTH_NODES = {\"Riboflavin\",\"Ribo*\",\"AdsRibo\",\"FMN\",\"FAD\",\"FADH2\"}\n",
        "SYNTH_EDGES = [(u,v,gt,k,lbl) for (u,v,gt,k,lbl) in EDGES if (u!=\"Waste\") and (v in SYNTH_NODES or v==\"FAD\")]\n",
        "\n",
        "adj = defaultdict(list)\n",
        "edge_meta = {}\n",
        "for u,v,gt,k,lbl in SYNTH_EDGES:\n",
        "    adj[u].append(v)\n",
        "    edge_meta[(u,v)] = (gt,k,lbl)\n",
        "\n",
        "def enumerate_paths(start=\"Start\", goal=\"FAD\", max_len=10):\n",
        "    paths = []\n",
        "    stack = [(start, [start])]\n",
        "    while stack:\n",
        "        node, path = stack.pop()\n",
        "        if node == goal:\n",
        "            paths.append(path)\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        if len(path) >= max_len:\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        for nxt in adj.get(node, []):\n",
        "            if nxt in path:\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "            stack.append((nxt, path + [nxt]))\n",
        "    return paths\n",
        "\n",
        "paths = enumerate_paths()\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# AOI route scoring\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                 seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                 seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "    W = {e: 0.0 for e in edge_meta.keys()}\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            wet, uv = gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                                  refuge=refuge)\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "            wet_on = 1.0 if gate == \"A\" else 0.0\n",
        "            uv_on  = 1.0 if gate == \"B\" else 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "            wet_eff = wet_on * wet\n",
        "            uv_eff  = uv_on  * uv\n",
        "\n",
        "            for (u,v),(gt,k,lbl) in edge_meta.items():\n",
        "                g = wet_eff if gt==\"wet\" else (uv_eff if gt==\"uv\" else 1.0)\n",
        "                W[(u,v)] += k * g * dt\n",
        "    return W\n",
        "\n",
        "def path_score(path, W):\n",
        "    s = 1.0\n",
        "    for i in range(len(path)-1):\n",
        "        s *= W[(path[i], path[i+1])]\n",
        "    return s\n",
        "\n",
        "def run_routes(env_label, env_kwargs):\n",
        "    W_AB = edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "    W_BA = edge_weights(protocol=\"BA\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "\n",
        "    rows = []\n",
        "    for p in paths:\n",
        "        s_ab = path_score(p, W_AB)\n",
        "        s_ba = path_score(p, W_BA)\n",
        "        rows.append({\n",
        "            \"env\": env_label,\n",
        "            \"route\": \" -> \".join(p),\n",
        "            \"S_AB\": s_ab,\n",
        "            \"S_BA\": s_ba,\n",
        "            \"Delta\": s_ab - s_ba,\n",
        "            \"Ratio_AB_over_BA\": (s_ab / s_ba) if s_ba > 0 else np.inf\n",
        "        })\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Environments (same as before)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "envs = {\n",
        "    \"equator_exposed\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0),\n",
        "    \"refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                   seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                   seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "    \"wet_season_refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                              seasonal_wet_amp=0.6, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "all_df = pd.concat([run_routes(name, kwargs) for name, kwargs in envs.items()], ignore_index=True)\n",
        "all_df.to_csv(\"FAD_routes_AOI_scores_prebiotic.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Saved: FAD_routes_AOI_scores_prebiotic.csv\\n\")\n",
        "for env in envs.keys():\n",
        "    sub = all_df[all_df[\"env\"] == env].sort_values(\"Delta\", ascending=False).head(10)\n",
        "    print(f\"=== Top routes by AOI advantage in {env} ===\")\n",
        "    print(sub[[\"route\",\"S_AB\",\"S_BA\",\"Delta\",\"Ratio_AB_over_BA\"]].to_string(index=False))\n",
        "    print()"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from collections import defaultdict\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Gates\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period=365, amp=0.0, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(day/period) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(step/steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                seasonal_wet_amp=0.0,\n",
        "                refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    uv  = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2)  # optional wet season\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Expanded flavin photochemistry + capture graph (hypothesis set)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Nodes:\n",
        "#   RF   : riboflavin-like\n",
        "#   RFT  : RF triplet/excited (activated)\n",
        "#   RFsq : semiquinone/radical-like activated form\n",
        "#   CDRF : cyclodehydroriboflavin (photoaddition product)\n",
        "#   LC/LF: lumichrome/lumiflavin (photolysis products)\n",
        "#   AdsRF: adsorption-protected RF\n",
        "#   FMN  : FMN-like\n",
        "#   FAD  : FAD-like\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Edge = (src, dst, gate_type, k, note)\n",
        "# gate_type: \"wet\", \"uv\", or \"none\"\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Notes:\n",
        "# - UV branches: RF -> CDRF / LC / LF are well-supported photochemical channels. 5\n",
        "# - Activated transient states exist (triplet, semiquinone radicals). 6\n",
        "# - Phosphate-species dependence motivates treating \"wet\" as capture/ionic window. 7\n",
        "\n",
        "EDGES = [\n",
        "    # Baseline precursor formation (placeholder for upstream flavin emergence)\n",
        "    (\"Start\", \"RF\",   \"wet\", 0.08, \"formation\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV activation to transient states (Ribo*)\n",
        "    (\"RF\", \"RFT\",  \"uv\",  0.06, \"triplet/excited\"),\n",
        "    (\"RFT\",\"RFsq\", \"uv\",  0.05, \"radical/semiquinone\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV photochemistry branches (stable photoproduct classes)\n",
        "    (\"RF\", \"CDRF\", \"uv\",  0.05, \"photoaddition->CDRF\"),\n",
        "    (\"RF\", \"LC\",   \"uv\",  0.05, \"photolysis->LC\"),\n",
        "    (\"RF\", \"LF\",   \"uv\",  0.03, \"photolysis->LF\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Wet capture steps (hypotheses): activated/transformed RF feeds onward chemistry\n",
        "    (\"RFsq\", \"FMN\", \"wet\", 0.12, \"capture_to_FMN_like\"),\n",
        "    (\"CDRF\", \"FMN\", \"wet\", 0.10, \"CDRF_capture_to_FMN_like\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Adsorption protection: wet hides RF in AdsRF; UV damage greatly reduced while adsorbed\n",
        "    (\"RF\",    \"AdsRF\", \"wet\", 0.10, \"adsorb\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsRF\", \"RF\",    \"wet\", 0.06, \"desorb\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsRF\", \"Waste\", \"uv\",  0.002,\"uv_damage_low_adsorbed\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Canonical late steps (template): RF->FMN->FAD (enzyme-free proxy)\n",
        "    (\"RF\",  \"FMN\", \"wet\", 0.06, \"direct_to_FMN_like\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\", \"FAD\", \"wet\", 0.06, \"to_FAD_like\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV damage sinks (penalties)\n",
        "    (\"RF\",  \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.02, \"uv_damage_RF\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.02, \"uv_damage_FMN\"),\n",
        "    (\"FAD\", \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.01, \"uv_damage_FAD\"),\n",
        "    (\"LC\",  \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.01, \"uv_damage_LC\"),\n",
        "    (\"LF\",  \"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.01, \"uv_damage_LF\"),\n",
        "    (\"CDRF\",\"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.01, \"uv_damage_CDRF\"),\n",
        "    (\"RFsq\",\"Waste\", \"uv\", 0.02, \"uv_damage_RFsq\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Mild recycling (optional)\n",
        "    (\"Waste\",\"Start\",\"wet\",0.01, \"recycle_pool\"),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Enumerate synthesis routes Start -> FAD\n",
        "# (only include edges that can move forward toward FAD; ignore Waste sinks for route enumeration)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "SYNTH_TARGET = \"FAD\"\n",
        "SYNTH_NODES = {\"Start\",\"RF\",\"RFT\",\"RFsq\",\"CDRF\",\"LC\",\"LF\",\"AdsRF\",\"FMN\",\"FAD\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "SYNTH_EDGES = [(u,v,gt,k,note) for (u,v,gt,k,note) in EDGES\n",
        "               if (u in SYNTH_NODES and v in SYNTH_NODES and v != \"Waste\")]\n",
        "\n",
        "adj = defaultdict(list)\n",
        "edge_meta = {}\n",
        "for u,v,gt,k,note in SYNTH_EDGES:\n",
        "    adj[u].append(v)\n",
        "    edge_meta[(u,v)] = (gt,k,note)\n",
        "\n",
        "def enumerate_paths(start=\"Start\", goal=\"FAD\", max_len=12):\n",
        "    paths = []\n",
        "    stack = [(start, [start])]\n",
        "    while stack:\n",
        "        node, path = stack.pop()\n",
        "        if node == goal:\n",
        "            paths.append(path)\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        if len(path) >= max_len:\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        for nxt in adj.get(node, []):\n",
        "            if nxt in path:\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "            stack.append((nxt, path + [nxt]))\n",
        "    return paths\n",
        "\n",
        "paths = enumerate_paths()\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# AOI edge weights W_e under AB vs BA\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                 seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                 seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "    W = {e: 0.0 for e in edge_meta.keys()}\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            wet, uv = gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                                  refuge=refuge)\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "            wet_on = 1.0 if gate == \"A\" else 0.0\n",
        "            uv_on  = 1.0 if gate == \"B\" else 0.0\n",
        "            wet_eff = wet_on * wet\n",
        "            uv_eff  = uv_on  * uv\n",
        "\n",
        "            for (u,v),(gt,k,note) in edge_meta.items():\n",
        "                g = wet_eff if gt == \"wet\" else (uv_eff if gt == \"uv\" else 1.0)\n",
        "                W[(u,v)] += k * g * dt\n",
        "    return W\n",
        "\n",
        "def path_score(path, W):\n",
        "    s = 1.0\n",
        "    for i in range(len(path)-1):\n",
        "        s *= W[(path[i], path[i+1])]\n",
        "    return s\n",
        "\n",
        "def run_routes(env_label, env_kwargs):\n",
        "    W_AB = edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "    W_BA = edge_weights(protocol=\"BA\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "\n",
        "    rows = []\n",
        "    for p in paths:\n",
        "        s_ab = path_score(p, W_AB)\n",
        "        s_ba = path_score(p, W_BA)\n",
        "        rows.append({\n",
        "            \"env\": env_label,\n",
        "            \"route\": \" -> \".join(p),\n",
        "            \"S_AB\": s_ab,\n",
        "            \"S_BA\": s_ba,\n",
        "            \"Delta\": s_ab - s_ba,\n",
        "            \"Ratio_AB_over_BA\": (s_ab / s_ba) if s_ba > 0 else np.inf\n",
        "        })\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Environments\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "envs = {\n",
        "    \"equator_exposed\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0),\n",
        "    \"refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                   seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                   seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "    \"wet_season_refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                              seasonal_wet_amp=0.6, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "all_df = pd.concat([run_routes(name, kwargs) for name, kwargs in envs.items()], ignore_index=True)\n",
        "all_df.to_csv(\"FAD_routes_AOI_scores_expanded_flavin_graph.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Saved: FAD_routes_AOI_scores_expanded_flavin_graph.csv\\n\")\n",
        "for env in envs.keys():\n",
        "    sub = all_df[all_df[\"env\"] == env].sort_values(\"Delta\", ascending=False).head(12)\n",
        "    print(f\"=== Top routes by AOI advantage in {env} ===\")\n",
        "    print(sub[[\"route\",\"S_AB\",\"S_BA\",\"Delta\",\"Ratio_AB_over_BA\"]].to_string(index=False))\n",
        "    print()"

      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from collections import Counter, defaultdict\n",
        "\n",
        "CSV_PATH = \"FAD_routes_AOI_scores_expanded_flavin_graph.csv\"\n",
        "\n",
        "df = pd.read_csv(CSV_PATH)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Basic sanity\n",
        "needed = {\"env\", \"route\", \"S_AB\", \"S_BA\", \"Delta\", \"Ratio_AB_over_BA\"}\n",
        "missing = needed - set(df.columns)\n",
        "if missing:\n",
        "    raise ValueError(f\"Missing columns in CSV: {missing}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def parse_nodes(route_str):\n",
        "    return [s.strip() for s in route_str.split(\"->\")]\n",
        "\n",
        "def parse_edges(nodes):\n",
        "    return list(zip(nodes[:-1], nodes[1:]))\n",
        "\n",
        "def summarize_env(sub, top_n=50):\n",
        "    # Top routes by Delta\n",
        "    top = sub.sort_values(\"Delta\", ascending=False).head(top_n).copy()\n",
        "\n",
        "    node_counts = Counter()\n",
        "    edge_counts = Counter()\n",
        "    motif_counts = Counter()\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Collect stats over top routes\n",
        "    for r in top[\"route\"].tolist():\n",
        "        nodes = parse_nodes(r)\n",
        "        edges = parse_edges(nodes)\n",
        "        node_counts.update(nodes)\n",
        "        edge_counts.update(edges)\n",
        "\n",
        "        # motifs you likely care about\n",
        "        if \"RFT\" in nodes and \"RFsq\" in nodes:\n",
        "            motif_counts[\"triplet->semiquinone (RFT→RFsq) present\"] += 1\n",
        "        if \"CDRF\" in nodes:\n",
        "            motif_counts[\"CDRF present\"] += 1\n",
        "        if \"AdsRF\" in nodes:\n",
        "            motif_counts[\"AdsRF present\"] += 1\n",
        "        if nodes == [\"Start\", \"RF\", \"FMN\", \"FAD\"]:\n",
        "            motif_counts[\"canonical wet-only path\"] += 1\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Aggregate a few useful route-level summaries\n",
        "    summary = {\n",
        "        \"topN\": top_n,\n",
        "        \"best_route\": top.iloc[0][\"route\"],\n",
        "        \"best_Delta\": float(top.iloc[0][\"Delta\"]),\n",
        "        \"best_ratio\": float(top.iloc[0][\"Ratio_AB_over_BA\"]),\n",
        "        \"mean_Delta_topN\": float(top[\"Delta\"].mean()),\n",
        "        \"median_Delta_topN\": float(top[\"Delta\"].median()),\n",
        "        \"num_unique_routes_topN\": int(top[\"route\"].nunique()),\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "    return top, summary, node_counts, edge_counts, motif_counts\n",
        "\n",
        "# Run for each environment\n",
        "envs = sorted(df[\"env\"].unique().tolist())\n",
        "\n",
        "all_summaries = []\n",
        "all_motifs = []\n",
        "\n",
        "for env in envs:\n",
        "    sub = df[df[\"env\"] == env].copy()\n",
        "\n",
        "    top, summary, node_counts, edge_counts, motif_counts = summarize_env(sub, top_n=50)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*80)\n",
        "    print(\"ENV:\", env)\n",
        "    print(\"Summary:\", summary)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"\\nTop 10 routes by Delta:\")\n",
        "    print(top[[\"route\", \"S_AB\", \"S_BA\", \"Delta\", \"Ratio_AB_over_BA\"]].head(10).to_string(index=False))\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"\\nMotif counts within top 50:\")\n",
        "    for k,v in motif_counts.items():\n",
        "        print(f\"  {k}: {v} / 50\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"\\nMost common nodes (top 12):\")\n",
        "    for node, cnt in node_counts.most_common(12):\n",
        "        print(f\"  {node}: {cnt}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"\\nMost common edges (top 12):\")\n",
        "    for (u,v), cnt in edge_counts.most_common(12):\n",
        "        print(f\"  {u} → {v}: {cnt}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # save per-env tables\n",
        "    top.to_csv(f\"top_routes_{env}.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "    all_summaries.append({\"env\": env, **summary})\n",
        "    for k,v in motif_counts.items():\n",
        "        all_motifs.append({\"env\": env, \"motif\": k, \"count_in_top50\": v})\n",
        "\n",
        "# Save rollups\n",
        "pd.DataFrame(all_summaries).to_csv(\"env_route_summaries.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "pd.DataFrame(all_motifs).to_csv(\"env_motif_counts.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\nSaved:\")\n",
        "print(\"  top_routes_<env>.csv for each env\")\n",
        "print(\"  env_route_summaries.csv\")\n",
        "print(\"  env_motif_counts.csv\")\n"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from collections import defaultdict\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Gates\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def seasonal(day, period=365, amp=0.0, phase=0.0):\n",
        "    return 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(day/period) + phase)\n",
        "\n",
        "def diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=1.0, phase=-np.pi/2):\n",
        "    raw = 1.0 + amp * np.sin(2*np.pi*(step/steps_per_day) + phase)\n",
        "    return max(0.0, raw)\n",
        "\n",
        "def gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    uv  = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_uv_amp) * diurnal(step, steps_per_day, amp=diurnal_uv_amp) * refuge\n",
        "    wet = seasonal(day, amp=seasonal_wet_amp, phase=np.pi/2)  # optional wet season\n",
        "    return wet, uv\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Expanded flavin graph with sinks\n",
        "# Nodes:\n",
        "#   RF     : riboflavin-like\n",
        "#   RFT    : excited/triplet-like\n",
        "#   RFsq   : radical/semiquinone-like\n",
        "#   CDRF   : cyclodehydroriboflavin-like photoaddition product\n",
        "#   LC/LF  : lumichrome/lumiflavin sinks (photoproducts)\n",
        "#   AdsRF/AdsFMN/AdsFAD : adsorption-protected states\n",
        "#   FMN/FAD : FMN-like and FAD-like\n",
        "#   Dead   : irreversible sink\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Edge fields:\n",
        "#   (src, dst, gate_type, k, note)\n",
        "# gate_type: \"wet\", \"uv\", \"none\"\n",
        "# k is a base propensity (dimensionless here; used in integrated W_e)\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "EDGES = [\n",
        "    # formation\n",
        "    (\"Start\", \"RF\",   \"wet\", 0.08, \"formation_pool\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV activation branch (AOI backbone)\n",
        "    (\"RF\",  \"RFT\",  \"uv\",  0.06, \"excitation\"),\n",
        "    (\"RFT\", \"RFsq\", \"uv\",  0.05, \"radicalize\"),\n",
        "    (\"RFsq\",\"FMN\",  \"wet\", 0.12, \"capture_to_FMN_like\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV photoaddition branch (secondary AOI backbone)\n",
        "    (\"RF\",   \"CDRF\", \"uv\",  0.05, \"photoaddition_to_CDRF\"),\n",
        "    (\"CDRF\", \"FMN\",  \"wet\", 0.10, \"CDRF_capture_to_FMN_like\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Canonical wet-only path (control)\n",
        "    (\"RF\",  \"FMN\", \"wet\", 0.06, \"direct_to_FMN_like\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\", \"FAD\", \"wet\", 0.06, \"to_FAD_like\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # -------------------------\n",
        "    # SINKS: lumichrome/lumiflavin formation under UV\n",
        "    # -------------------------\n",
        "    (\"RF\", \"LC\", \"uv\", 0.08, \"photolysis_to_lumichrome\"),\n",
        "    (\"RF\", \"LF\", \"uv\", 0.04, \"photolysis_to_lumiflavin\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # sink decay to Dead under UV\n",
        "    (\"LC\", \"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.03, \"LC_to_dead\"),\n",
        "    (\"LF\", \"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.03, \"LF_to_dead\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # optional low wet recycling (turn this down/up to test robustness)\n",
        "    (\"LC\", \"RF\", \"wet\", 0.003, \"LC_recycle_to_RF\"),\n",
        "    (\"LF\", \"RF\", \"wet\", 0.002, \"LF_recycle_to_RF\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # -------------------------\n",
        "    # Adsorption protection (wet): hide species to reduce UV loss\n",
        "    # We represent protection by moving into Ads* nodes.\n",
        "    # -------------------------\n",
        "    (\"RF\",   \"AdsRF\",  \"wet\", 0.10, \"adsorb_RF\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsRF\",\"RF\",     \"wet\", 0.06, \"desorb_RF\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\",  \"AdsFMN\", \"wet\", 0.08, \"adsorb_FMN\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsFMN\",\"FMN\",   \"wet\", 0.05, \"desorb_FMN\"),\n",
        "    (\"FAD\",  \"AdsFAD\", \"wet\", 0.06, \"adsorb_FAD\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsFAD\",\"FAD\",   \"wet\", 0.04, \"desorb_FAD\"),\n",
        "\n",
        "    # UV losses (lower in Ads states)\n",
        "    (\"RF\",    \"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.01,  \"RF_uv_loss\"),\n",
        "    (\"FMN\",   \"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.015, \"FMN_uv_loss\"),\n",
        "    (\"FAD\",   \"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.01,  \"FAD_uv_loss\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsRF\", \"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.001, \"AdsRF_uv_loss_low\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsFMN\",\"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.001, \"AdsFMN_uv_loss_low\"),\n",
        "    (\"AdsFAD\",\"Dead\", \"uv\", 0.001, \"AdsFAD_uv_loss_low\"),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Nodes included for routing (exclude Dead as terminal)\n",
        "NODES = sorted({u for (u,_,_,_,_) in EDGES} | {v for (_,v,_,_,_) in EDGES})\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Enumerate simple routes Start -> FAD through allowed nodes\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "ALLOWED_NODES = set(NODES) - {\"Dead\"}  # allow sinks, but not the terminal dead node in routes\n",
        "TARGET = \"FAD\"\n",
        "\n",
        "adj = defaultdict(list)\n",
        "edge_meta = {}\n",
        "for (u,v,gt,k,note) in EDGES:\n",
        "    if (u in ALLOWED_NODES) and (v in ALLOWED_NODES):\n",
        "        adj[u].append(v)\n",
        "        edge_meta[(u,v)] = (gt, float(k), note)\n",
        "\n",
        "def enumerate_paths(start=\"Start\", goal=\"FAD\", max_len=14):\n",
        "    paths = []\n",
        "    stack = [(start, [start])]\n",
        "    while stack:\n",
        "        node, path = stack.pop()\n",
        "        if node == goal:\n",
        "            paths.append(path)\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        if len(path) >= max_len:\n",
        "            continue\n",
        "        for nxt in adj.get(node, []):\n",
        "            if nxt in path:\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "            stack.append((nxt, path + [nxt]))\n",
        "    return paths\n",
        "\n",
        "paths = enumerate_paths()\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Compute AOI-weighted edge weights W_e under AB or BA\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                 seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                 seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0):\n",
        "    dt = 1.0 / steps_per_day\n",
        "    half = steps_per_day // 2\n",
        "    W = {e: 0.0 for e in edge_meta.keys()}\n",
        "\n",
        "    for day in range(days):\n",
        "        for step in range(steps_per_day):\n",
        "            wet, uv = gate_values(day, step, steps_per_day,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_uv_amp=seasonal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  diurnal_uv_amp=diurnal_uv_amp,\n",
        "                                  seasonal_wet_amp=seasonal_wet_amp,\n",
        "                                  refuge=refuge)\n",
        "            gate = protocol[0] if step < half else protocol[1]\n",
        "            wet_on = 1.0 if gate == \"A\" else 0.0\n",
        "            uv_on  = 1.0 if gate == \"B\" else 0.0\n",
        "            wet_eff = wet_on * wet\n",
        "            uv_eff  = uv_on  * uv\n",
        "\n",
        "            for (u,v),(gt,k,note) in edge_meta.items():\n",
        "                g = wet_eff if gt == \"wet\" else (uv_eff if gt == \"uv\" else 1.0)\n",
        "                W[(u,v)] += k * g * dt\n",
        "\n",
        "    return W\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Turn weights into transition probabilities at each node:\n",
        "# P(u->v) = W(u,v) / sum_out W(u,*)\n",
        "# This is what makes sinks \"steal probability mass\".\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "def transition_probs(W):\n",
        "    out_sum = defaultdict(float)\n",
        "    for (u,v), w in W.items():\n",
        "        out_sum[u] += w\n",
        "\n",
        "    P = {}\n",
        "    for (u,v), w in W.items():\n",
        "        denom = out_sum[u]\n",
        "        P[(u,v)] = (w / denom) if denom > 0 else 0.0\n",
        "    return P\n",
        "\n",
        "def path_prob(path, P):\n",
        "    p = 1.0\n",
        "    for i in range(len(path)-1):\n",
        "        p *= P[(path[i], path[i+1])]\n",
        "    return p\n",
        "\n",
        "def run_routes(env_label, env_kwargs):\n",
        "    W_AB = edge_weights(protocol=\"AB\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "    W_BA = edge_weights(protocol=\"BA\", **env_kwargs)\n",
        "    P_AB = transition_probs(W_AB)\n",
        "    P_BA = transition_probs(W_BA)\n",
        "\n",
        "    rows = []\n",
        "    for p in paths:\n",
        "        pab = path_prob(p, P_AB)\n",
        "        pba = path_prob(p, P_BA)\n",
        "        rows.append({\n",
        "            \"env\": env_label,\n",
        "            \"route\": \" -> \".join(p),\n",
        "            \"P_AB\": pab,\n",
        "            \"P_BA\": pba,\n",
        "            \"DeltaP\": pab - pba,\n",
        "            \"Ratio_AB_over_BA\": (pab / pba) if pba > 0 else np.inf,\n",
        "        })\n",
        "    return pd.DataFrame(rows)\n",
        "\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "# Environments\n",
        "# -------------------------\n",
        "envs = {\n",
        "    \"equator_exposed\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                            seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                            seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=1.0),\n",
        "    \"refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                   seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                   seasonal_wet_amp=0.0, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "    \"wet_season_refuge\": dict(days=365, steps_per_day=200,\n",
        "                              seasonal_uv_amp=0.6, diurnal_uv_amp=1.0,\n",
        "                              seasonal_wet_amp=0.6, refuge=0.3),\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "all_df = pd.concat([run_routes(name, kwargs) for name, kwargs in envs.items()], ignore_index=True)\n",
        "all_df.to_csv(\"FAD_routes_AOI_scores_sinkaware.csv\", index=False)\n",
        "print(\"Saved: FAD_routes_AOI_scores_sinkaware.csv\\n\")\n",
        "\n",
        "for env in envs:\n",
        "    sub = all_df[all_df[\"env\"] == env].sort_values(\"DeltaP\", ascending=False).head(12)\n",
        "    print(f\"=== Top routes by AOI advantage (DeltaP) in {env} ===\")\n",
        "    print(sub[[\"route\",\"P_AB\",\"P_BA\",\"DeltaP\",\"Ratio_AB_over_BA\"]].to_string(index=False))\n",
        "    print()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "CveR1LwHOV_c",
        "outputId": "f8bd972a-c38f-4379-8bdd-5f598dd971d2",
